## Quick Start

1. Copy and configure environment variables:

   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   # Edit .env with your Datadog API key and site
   ```

2. Start the stack:

   ```bash
   docker compose up -d
   ```

3. Verify services are running:

   ```bash
   curl http://localhost:8080/health
   ```

